cafes.name: don't stress meowt - Cat Cafe
cafes.address: 1900 Linwood Blvd Suite 300, Oklahoma City, OK 73106, USA

text.text: This is one of my favorite places to go when I am in need of a pick me up. Even if you don't enter the cat room the atmosphere in the cafe is still wonderful, and you still get to see the kitties! They have an excellent cat themed shop and local cat artwork and best of all they are saving lives and helping the kitties find their forever homes.

I love the cat cafe and highly recommend!!! It’s got me through some of the hardest days and some of the best of days! Their hot chocolate is absolutely amazing, not to mention if you reserve online you can cuddle and play with the cats!

We brought our 6 and 9 year old and they were in HEAVEN! The kitties were very friendly! There were just over 20 cats (I think) in the lounge and we were in there with one other family. Plenty of cats to go around. The lounge has glass walls so if a member of your group isn’t interested in going in the lounge they can still see the action easily. You do sign a waiver and there are some rules, pretty much what you’d expect. We got lots of tokens for treats which is the best way to interact with the cats. This was a really special activity for our family. I think it would be great if you’re looking to adopt a cat as you get plenty of time to learn their personalities and bond.
